jobs_results.description:
1. Design consumer facing features to shape shopping experience on TikTok;
2. Prioritize and build product features, through continuous iteration and experimentation;
3. Dive deep into user needs, conduct user research & analysis to conceptualize and build products that are aligned with business goals while ensuring a seamless, intuitive shopping experience;
4. Own consumer facing products end-to-end, including ideation, design, build, test, launch, and measure post-launch;
5. Work cross-functionally, build synergy and influence with multiple departments, globally.
1. Bachelor's degree or above;
2. Minimum 2 years of product management at a e-commerce company;
3. Excellent communication skills, can clearly describe the vision, planning and problem; and coordinate with other teams to solve it together in depth;
4. Analytical and data-driven, knows how to use data to identify problems, find opportunities, and drive continuous improvement in product;
5. Demonstrated ability to operate in... fast-paced, entrepreneurial environments, able to deal with rapid changes and imperfect status quo;
6. Has a global vision and enthusiasm, and pays continuous attention to global internet products
